<a href="http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=4458522"><span class="caps">NPR</span> : Firings Raise Questions of Blogger Freedoms</a>: "Day to Day, January 19, 2005: Can blogging about your work get you canned? <span class="caps">NPR</span>'s Eric Weiner reports on people who have been fired from their jobs because they maintain Web logs about their work. The firings raise questions about the rights of bloggers."<br /><br />Check it out for an interview with Heather of <a href=http://www.dooce.com>Dooce</a>